/wiki/Matt_Walker_(soccer): Matthew Thomas Walker ( born September 16 , 1992 ) is an American former professional soccer player .
/wiki/Agust\u00edn_Viana: Agustín Viana ( born 23 August 1983 in Chicago ) is an American-born Uruguayan former professional footballer .
/wiki/Daniel_Paladini: Daniel Paladini ( born November 11 , 1984 in Northridge , California ) is an American soccer player .
/wiki/Fifi_Baiden: Kingsley Mensah Fifi Baiden ( born November 11 , 1991 ) is a Ghanaian former professional footballer who is currently a coach with the UC Santa Barbara Gauchos men 's soccer team .
/wiki/Matt_Wiet: Matthew Wiet ( born September 23 , 1990 ) is an American former soccer player who last played for the Columbus Crew in Major League Soccer .
/wiki/Ross_Friedman_(soccer): Ross Benjamin Friedman ( born January 8 , 1992 ) is an American former professional soccer player who played for the Columbus Crew and the Dayton Dutch Lions as a defender .
/wiki/Josh_Williams_(soccer): Josh Williams ( born April 18 , 1988 ) is an American professional soccer player who plays for MLS club Columbus Crew SC as a defender .
/wiki/Allocation_money: In Major League Soccer , allocation money represents an amount of money teams can use to sign players and/or allocate to their salaries to get under the salary cap .
/wiki/Bernardo_A\u00f1or: Bernardo Añor Acosta ( ; born May 24 , 1988 ) is a Venezuelan footballer who plays as a defender or a midfielder for Caracas of the Venezuelan Primera División .
/wiki/Jairo_Arrieta: Jairo Arrieta Obando ( born 25 August 1983 ) is a Costa Rican footballer , who plays as a forward for A.D. San Carlos .
/wiki/2014_MLS_Expansion_Draft: The 2014 MLS Expansion Draft was a special draft for the Major League Soccer expansion teams New York City FC and Orlando City SC . As determined by a Priority Draft conducted September 24 , 2014 , Orlando City SC selected first . The draft was conducted by conference call at 2:00 pm EST ( UTC-5 ) on December 10 , 2014 .
/wiki/Eric_Gehrig: Eric Otto Gehrig ( born December 25 , 1987 ) is an American former soccer player who was most recently an assistant coach for Chicago Fire of MLS .
/wiki/Ben_Sweat: Ben Sweat ( born September 4 , 1991 ) is an American soccer player who currently plays for Inter Miami in Major League Soccer .
/wiki/Hern\u00e1n_Grana: Hernán Gustavo Grana ( born 12 April 1985 ) is an Argentine football defender currently playing for Ferro Carril Oeste .
/wiki/Kalen_Ryden: Kalen Ryden ( born April 12 , 1991 ) is an American soccer player who currently plays for New Mexico United in the USL Championship .
/wiki/Adam_Bedell: Adam Bedell ( born December 1 , 1991 ) is an American professional soccer player who plays as a forward .
/wiki/2016_MLS_SuperDraft: The 2016 MLS SuperDraft was the seventeenth SuperDraft conducted by Major League Soccer . The SuperDraft is held each year in conjunction with the annual National Soccer Coaches Association of America convention . The 2016 convention was held in Baltimore , Maryland . The first two rounds of the 2016 SuperDraft were held on January 14 , 2016 . Rounds three and four were held via conference call on January 19 , 2016 .
